The CI Messenger is a simple server socket application that visualizes build statuses sent from CI servers.

Supported CI servers:
 * Jenkins / Hudson with Notification Plugin (https://wiki.jenkins-ci.org/display/JENKINS/Notification+Plugin)
 

Technology used:
 * Scala 2.9.0
 * Maven 3.0.3

How to run:
 java -jar ci-messenger-0.0.1-SNAPSHOT-jar-with-dependencies.jar 